OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDaytime
OL,6,Fshowers will become increasingly
OL,7,Fconfined to coasts in the north this
OL,8,Fevening, leading to a dry and clear
OL,9,Fnight for many. Turning chilly under
OL,10,Fthe clear skies with a fairly
OL,11,Fwidespread frost, although clouding
OL,12,Fover in the west later.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FA chilly start, but mostly dry
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells. Cloud will continue
OL,16,Fto increase across western areas
OL,17,Fthrough the day, with outbreaks of
OL,18,Frain reaching the far northwest later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
